Program: Great Lives
Title: Joe Slovo
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00lyfm8
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 14 Jul 2017
Matthew Parris presents the biographical series in which his guests choose someone who has inspired their lives. David Miliband discusses the life of Joe Slovo, a leading member of the African National Congress and the first housing minister in Nelson Mandela's government. Slovo's daughter, Gillian, joins in the discussion. Show less